'''水果帶'''（{{lang-en|Fruit Belt}}）是美國一個[[微氣候|微氣候]]上適合種植[[水果|水果]]的帶狀地區，明顯集中於[[五大湖|五大湖]]區，包括[[西密西根|西密西根]]、{{Link-en|北密西根|Northern Michigan}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Fruit Growing Conditions |accessdate=2011-08-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080908043851/http://www.michiganfruitbelt.org/fruitgrowing.htm |archivedate=2008-09-08 |work=Southwest Michigan Fruit Belt Project |url=http://www.michiganfruitbelt.org/fruitgrowing.htm |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.michigan.gov/dnr/0,1607,7-153-54463_19313_20652_19271_19357-176851--,00.html|title=Michigan Department of Natural Resources|language=en|accessdate=2013-12-01|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202224526/http://www.michigan.gov/dnr/0,1607,7-153-54463_19313_20652_19271_19357-176851--,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.michmarkers.com/startup.asp?startpage=S0155.htm|title=The Fruit Belt|publisher=Michigan Department of Natural Resources and Environment|language=en|accessdate=2010-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302041709/http://www.michmarkers.com/startup.asp?startpage=S0155.htm|archive-date=2012-03-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和[[伊利湖|伊利湖]]南岸<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.concordgrapebelt.org/tourism/|title=Lake Erie Concord Grape Belt: Concord Grape Belt Tourism|publisher=Concord Grape Belt Heritage Association|language=en|accessdate=2013-04-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112025750/http://www.concordgrapebelt.org/tourism/|archivedate=2013-11-12}}</ref>。造成五大湖區特別適合種植水果的原因是[[大湖效應|大湖效應]]。另外，水果帶與雪帶大致上重疊。在美國的{{Link-en|中華盛頓|Central Washington}}地區，也同樣有個水果帶<ref>{{cite news |first=Paul J.C |last=Friedlander |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Circle of Beauty |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=888&dat=19770703&id=bPELAAAAIBAJ&sjid=6lkDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6496,1685721 |work=''New York Times'' |language=en |publisher= |date= |accessdate=2009-08-05 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>。

